{
  "stem": "2833.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She died in '44 and was 50 years old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So yeah, she was 47.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I started to work in an office, which was in charge of putting people to work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some people were-- in that office were running the men's division and some the women.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I worked for the head of the woman's division.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was because we had to supply everything that a little town needed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they took all the Czech people out of the-- of that town and gave us all the little houses.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because there were more and more people coming-- more transports.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we had to do our own bread baking, and we had to do our own laundry.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we had to do the big-- I mean, the you know, big-- not for one person, but for a whole-- barracks or so.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And all the labor had to be done by us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had to see that-- to put everybody to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then there was a lot of labor demanded by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had to make uniforms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had to build things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was a big place for-- where they-- I don't know, really, what they made.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But it was only out of wood-- whatever they made.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They made caskets for them, and they made all kind of-- and these people had to be selected and trained a little bit, and then sent to work for either the Germans or for running of the-- of Terezin.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Every kitchen had to feed about 20,000 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we had to do-- get the cooks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We had to get the people who transported materials within the little town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So everybody had to somehow get to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
